cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

The paper deals with improving visual place recognition and metric localization, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of a generator network and adversarial training also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of dense descriptor maps and benchmarking on a dataset suggests a connection to multimedia (cs.MM).
